<html>

<head>
    <title>
        <%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %>
    </title>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="wrap">
        <header>
            <div id="title">
                <img id="logo" class="invertible" src="<%= require('./assets/img/coffee.jpg') %>"
                    alt="coffee cup logo for the cafe" />
                <h1>
                    <%= htmlWebpackPlugin.options.title %>
                </h1>
                <div id="color-mode" class="form-control">
                    <label id="color-mode-light"><input type="radio" id="light-mode" name="color-mode" value="light"
                            checked>Light</label>
                    <label id="color-mode-dark"><input type="radio" id="dark-mode" name="color-mode"
                            value="dark">Dark</label>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="about-wrapper" class="invertible">
                <div id="about" class="invertible">
                    <h2>Welcome to the home of tasty.</h2>
                    <p>Drinks, food, snacks.</p>
                    <p>Dine in or order to takeaway.</p>
                    <p>Serving delicious since 2020</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>
        <main id="menu">
            <div id="filter">
                <span>Filter:</span>
                <button id="filter-meals">Meals</button>
                <button id="filter-desserts">Desserts</button>
                <button id="filter-drinks">Drinks</button>
            </div>
            <h2 id="menu-title">The menu</h2>
            <ul id="menu-list">
            </ul>
        </main>
        <section id="alergens">
            <h2>Alergen info</h2>
            <p class="important">All food is prepared in a shared kitchen so we cannot guarantee the absence of
                alergens.
            </p>
            <p>The 14 allergens are: celery, cereals containing gluten (such as wheat, barley and oats), crustaceans
                (such
                as prawns, crabs and lobsters), eggs, fish, lupin, milk, molluscs (such as mussels and oysters),
                mustard,
                peanuts, sesame, soybeans, sulphur dioxide and sulphites (if the sulphur dioxide and sulphites are at a
                concentration of more than ten parts per million) and tree nuts (such as almonds, hazelnuts, walnuts,
                brazil
                nuts, cashews, pecans, pistachios and macadamia nuts).</p>
            <p>This also applies to additives, processing aids and any other substances which are present in the final
                product.</p>
            <p>Please ask your server for more details.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="contact">
            <h2>To reserve a table, please contact us</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <span>Email: <a href="mailto:thecafe@theinternet.com">thecafe@theinternet.com</a></span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Call: <a href="tel:123-456-7890">123-456-7890</a></span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section id="copyright">
            <p>
                <span id="cc-symbol">Â©</span>
                2020-2024 Tech Much Menu Design, Tech Much Menu Design Corp Inc.
            </p>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>

</html>